Unnamed: 16: Column A - Index = Molecule Number
Yellow columns B & K = not required
Green columns = required for analysis
Columns C-J are independent properties of the CORRESPONDING Molecule No. listed in column A
Columns L-O are results
Analysis - whether column L data depend upon sum of columns C-J data
Analysis - whether column M data depend upon sum of columns C-J data
Analysis - whether column N data depend upon sum of columns C-J data
Analysis - whether column O data depend upon sum of columns C-J data
Column K is not important and ignore
Column B is not important and ignore
MW = Molecular weight of molecule
#Atoms = Number of atoms in molecule
SlogP = Water solubility of molecule
TPSA = Total polar surface area of molecule
Flexibility = Conformational flexibility of molecule
#RB = Number of rotatable bonds in molecule
HBA = Hydrogen bond acceptor in molecule
HBD = Hydogen bond donor in molecule
Rof5 = Rule of 5

LF Rank score, LF dG, LF VS score, and LF LE are results of molecules that how good they bind with the disease target protein. More negative value means superior molecule in term of binding with the target protein
